title: Agent Yee Says He'd Start Auburn's Newton Versus Alabama: Video
description: Donald  Yee, agent for New England Patriots quarterback Tom Brady, says he would start Auburn University quarterback Cam Newton, a candidate for the Heisman Trophy, against Alabama this weekend. Lee also says allowing private-equity firms to operate college football programs would lead to beneficial "innovation" in the sport. Bloomberg's Michele Steele speaks. (Source: Bloomberg)
